Damn, they're persistent!

30
00:01:45,972 --> 00:01:49,008
Freeze! If you don't want to die, leave now!

31
00:01:49,008 --> 00:01:51,644
What are you trying to act cool for, Ryo?

32
00:01:51,644 --> 00:01:55,248
You can say lines like that after
you've paid off your debt.

33
00:01:55,248 --> 00:01:57,978
Anyway, I'll hang on to this as insurance.

34
00:01:59,018 --> 00:02:01,111
The tools of my trade!

35
