Even Kaori's Pissed!
Ryo & a Young Lady
~Pinch Hitter Marriage Story~

36
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:11,331
Damn it, this is what happens when you go
drinking when we don't have any money!

37
00:02:11,331 --> 00:02:15,468
We never have money because you
refuse every female client!

38
00:02:15,468 --> 00:02:19,165
What am I supposed to do without
the tools of my trade?!

39
00:02:19,806 --> 00:02:22,942
Man, I guess I've got no choice.

40
00:02:22,942 --> 00:02:26,105
I don't like it, but there's one client
who wants to hire us.

41
00:02:27,046 --> 00:02:30,617
The meeting is at 1 PM in the lobby
of the Oshiuri TV Station.

42
